Home of Droplets, a cloud storage client library.
Scality - http://www.scality.com

Droplets is open source and released under the GPLv2.

Mission: Help the transition to object based cloud storage by providing a structured API to simplify application developers job and address key user concerns. 

All source code is hosted here, documentation is also available here in the wiki section:
http://github.com/scality/Droplets/wiki
